title: Patient 11, female, adeno
characteristics_ch1.4: performance status corresponding to who criteria: 1
characteristics_ch1.9: days to recurrence / to last visit: 3223
extract_protocol_ch1: Five to ten sections (10µm) were cut from each frozen tissue block and collected into a tube with Buffer RLT (Qiagen, Hilden, Germany). Total RNA was extracted using the RNeasy Mini Kit following instructions from the manufacturer (Qiagen). RNA concentrations were measured with a ND-1000 spectrophotometer (NanoDrop Technologies, Wilmington, DE, U.S.A.), and the quality (RNA Integrity Number, RIN) was assessed using the Agilent 2100 Bioanalyzer system (Agilent Biotechnologies, Palo Alto, U.S.A.).
label_protocol_ch1: For each sample, 2µg of total RNA from each sample was used to prepare biotinylated fragmented cRNA for analysis on Affymetrix Human Genome U133 plus 2 arrays (54675 probe sets, Affymetrix Inc., Santa Clara, U.S.A.). Sample preparation, processing and hybridization were performed according to the GeneChip® Expression Analysis Technical Manual (Affymetrix Inc., Rev. 5).
hyb_protocol: For each sample, 2µg of total RNA from each sample was used to prepare biotinylated fragmented cRNA for analysis on Affymetrix Human Genome U133 plus 2 arrays (54675 probe sets, Affymetrix Inc., Santa Clara, U.S.A.). Sample preparation, processing and hybridization were performed according to the GeneChip® Expression Analysis Technical Manual (Affymetrix Inc., Rev. 5).
scan_protocol: The arrays were washed and stained using a Fluidics Station 450 and finally scanned using a GeneChip® Scanner 3000 7G.
description: gene expression data from non small lung cancer frozen sample of patient 11
data_processing: Biocondoctor affy package standard RMA preprocessing in Matrix Template

RNA concentrations were measured with a ND-1000 spectrophotometer (NanoDrop Technologies, Wilmington, DE, U.S.A.), and the quality (RNA Integrity Number, RIN) was assessed using the Agilent 2100 Bioanalyzer system (Agilent Biotechnologies, Palo Alto, U.S.A.).
label_protocol_ch1: For each sample, 2µg of total RNA from each sample was used to prepare biotinylated fragmented cRNA for analysis on Affymetrix Human Genome U133 plus 2 arrays (54675 probe sets, Affymetrix Inc., Santa Clara, U.S.A.). Sample preparation, processing and hybridization were performed according to the GeneChip® Expression Analysis Technical Manual (Affymetrix Inc., Rev. 5).
hyb_protocol: For each sample, 2µg of total RNA from each sample was used to prepare biotinylated fragmented cRNA for analysis on Affymetrix Human Genome U133 plus 2 arrays (54675 probe sets, Affymetrix Inc., Santa Clara, U.S.A.). Sample preparation, processing and hybridization were performed according to the GeneChip® Expression Analysis Technical Manual (Affymetrix Inc., Rev. 5).
scan_protocol: The arrays were washed and stained using a Fluidics Station 450 and finally scanned using a GeneChip® Scanner 3000 7G.
description: gene expression data from non small lung cancer frozen sample of patient 272
data_processing: Biocondoctor affy package standard RMA preprocessing in Matrix Template

RNA concentrations were measured with a ND-1000 spectrophotometer (NanoDrop Technologies, Wilmington, DE, U.S.A.), and the quality (RNA Integrity Number, RIN) was assessed using the Agilent 2100 Bioanalyzer system (Agilent Biotechnologies, Palo Alto, U.S.A.).
label_protocol_ch1: For each sample, 2µg of total RNA from each sample was used to prepare biotinylated fragmented cRNA for analysis on Affymetrix Human Genome U133 plus 2 arrays (54675 probe sets, Affymetrix Inc., Santa Clara, U.S.A.). Sample preparation, processing and hybridization were performed according to the GeneChip® Expression Analysis Technical Manual (Affymetrix Inc., Rev. 5).
hyb_protocol: For each sample, 2µg of total RNA from each sample was used to prepare biotinylated fragmented cRNA for analysis on Affymetrix Human Genome U133 plus 2 arrays (54675 probe sets, Affymetrix Inc., Santa Clara, U.S.A.). Sample preparation, processing and hybridization were performed according to the GeneChip® Expression Analysis Technical Manual (Affymetrix Inc., Rev. 5).
scan_protocol: The arrays were washed and stained using a Fluidics Station 450 and finally scanned using a GeneChip® Scanner 3000 7G.
description: gene expression data from non small lung cancer frozen sample of patient 373
data_processing: Biocondoctor affy package standard RMA preprocessing in Matrix Template

RNA concentrations were measured with a ND-1000 spectrophotometer (NanoDrop Technologies, Wilmington, DE, U.S.A.), and the quality (RNA Integrity Number, RIN) was assessed using the Agilent 2100 Bioanalyzer system (Agilent Biotechnologies, Palo Alto, U.S.A.).
label_protocol_ch1: For each sample, 2µg of total RNA from each sample was used to prepare biotinylated fragmented cRNA for analysis on Affymetrix Human Genome U133 plus 2 arrays (54675 probe sets, Affymetrix Inc., Santa Clara, U.S.A.). Sample preparation, processing and hybridization were performed according to the GeneChip® Expression Analysis Technical Manual (Affymetrix Inc., Rev. 5).
hyb_protocol: For each sample, 2µg of total RNA from each sample was used to prepare biotinylated fragmented cRNA for analysis on Affymetrix Human Genome U133 plus 2 arrays (54675 probe sets, Affymetrix Inc., Santa Clara, U.S.A.). Sample preparation, processing and hybridization were performed according to the GeneChip® Expression Analysis Technical Manual (Affymetrix Inc., Rev. 5).
scan_protocol: The arrays were washed and stained using a Fluidics Station 450 and finally scanned using a GeneChip® Scanner 3000 7G.
description: gene expression data from non small lung cancer frozen sample of patient 101
data_processing: Biocondoctor affy package standard RMA preprocessing in Matrix Template

RNA concentrations were measured with a ND-1000 spectrophotometer (NanoDrop Technologies, Wilmington, DE, U.S.A.), and the quality (RNA Integrity Number, RIN) was assessed using the Agilent 2100 Bioanalyzer system (Agilent Biotechnologies, Palo Alto, U.S.A.).
label_protocol_ch1: For each sample, 2µg of total RNA from each sample was used to prepare biotinylated fragmented cRNA for analysis on Affymetrix Human Genome U133 plus 2 arrays (54675 probe sets, Affymetrix Inc., Santa Clara, U.S.A.). Sample preparation, processing and hybridization were performed according to the GeneChip® Expression Analysis Technical Manual (Affymetrix Inc., Rev. 5).
hyb_protocol: For each sample, 2µg of total RNA from each sample was used to prepare biotinylated fragmented cRNA for analysis on Affymetrix Human Genome U133 plus 2 arrays (54675 probe sets, Affymetrix Inc., Santa Clara, U.S.A.). Sample preparation, processing and hybridization were performed according to the GeneChip® Expression Analysis Technical Manual (Affymetrix Inc., Rev. 5).
scan_protocol: The arrays were washed and stained using a Fluidics Station 450 and finally scanned using a GeneChip® Scanner 3000 7G.
description: gene expression data from non small lung cancer frozen sample of patient 226
data_processing: Biocondoctor affy package standard RMA preprocessing in Matrix Template
